Persistent Grafana data directory for local bind mounts.

This directory is mounted to `/var/lib/grafana` by:
- `industrial/moqui-postgres-compose.yml`
- `industrial/grafana-compose.yml`

Keep the directory in the repository so Docker bind mounts always have a target.
Do not commit generated Grafana runtime files from local executions.

This is also where Grafana persists:
- dashboard state created from the UI
- SQLite metadata in `grafana.db`
- any runtime plugin files downloaded by the local container

The deployment profile does not preinstall Grafana AI plugins by default.
If they are tested locally, remove their runtime directories from this bind
mount before committing repository changes.
